name: Rebel Tech
Lore: 'Del Goren, typical expert in communications and scanner jamming, served aboard the Rebel privateer corvette Spiral before joining the Alliance High Council.',
Text: 'When at your war room: Cumulatively adds 1 to total of Attack Run. OR Once during each of your control phases, may send this tech to your Used Pile and take Death Star: Trench into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
